# Claude Code — ALL project memory and chat context stays local.
# Claude Code auto-loads these files when working in this repo, but
# they should never reach GitHub. They contain server IPs, passwords,
# tokens, chat transcripts, and project notes that are only useful to
# the maintainer's local sessions.
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
CHAT-CONTEXT-DUMP*.md
.claude/sessions/
.claude/projects/
.claude/session-env/
